IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
PROGRAM-ID. datademo.
DATA DIVISION.
FILE SECTION.
FD CUST-FILE.
01 CUST-RECORD.
    05 CUST-ID PIC 9(5).
    05 CUST-NAME PIC X(20).
    05 FILLER PIC X(3).
SD SORT-FILE.
01 SORT-RECORD PIC X(80).
WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
01 COUNTER PIC 9(2) USAGE COMP-3 VALUE ZERO.
01 TOTAL PIC S9(5)V99 VALUE 0.
01 STATUS-FLAG PIC X VALUE "N".
    88 DONE VALUE "Y".
    88 IN-RANGE VALUE "A" THROUGH "M".
01 TABLE-DATA.
    05 ITEM OCCURS 1 TO 10 TIMES DEPENDING ON COUNTER
       INDEXED BY ITEM-IDX PIC 9(4).
01 ALT REDEFINES TABLE-DATA PIC X(40).
01 EDITED-FIELDS.
    05 F1 PIC X JUSTIFIED RIGHT.
    05 F2 PIC 9 BLANK WHEN ZERO.
    05 F3 PIC S9 SIGN IS LEADING SEPARATE.
    05 F4 PIC 9 SYNCHRONIZED LEFT.
    05 F5 PIC X GLOBAL.
    05 F6 PIC X EXTERNAL.
66 RENAME-FIELD RENAMES F1 THROUGH F2.
LOCAL-STORAGE SECTION.
01 LS-TEMP PIC 9(4).
LINKAGE SECTION.
01 LK-PARM PIC X(10).
PROCEDURE DIVISION.
    DISPLAY "running".
    STOP RUN.
